c1d9901c814.jpg\" title=\"640.webp.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp.jpg\"/></p><hr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/><p><br/></p>', 'LEE HOUSE', 'Design by East to West 東形西見设计', '3', '1', '2018-04-02 15:19:53', '', '0', '3', '', '0', '{\"thumb\":\"portal\\/20180402\\/5ac1d912500a6.JPG\",\"template\":\"\"}', '62', '0', '0', '0');
INSERT INTO `hi_posts` VALUES ('19', '1', '融侨水乡', '融侨水乡', '2018-01-10 00:54:35', '<p><img src=\"/data/upload/ueditor/20180410/5acc2616459ec.JPG\" title=\"1.JPG\" alt=\"1.JPG\" width=\"737\" height=\"373\" style=\"width: 737px; height: 373px;\"/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-indent: 32px;\">本案位于福州阳光城翡丽湾，庭前的入户花园摒去了城市的车水马龙。卸下喧嚣，踏青而入，一黄一黑两只造型简约的摆饰憨态可掬，入户门厅的家具在形色上使用差异对比的手法，又不失统一与质朴。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/data/upload/ueditor/20180402/5ac1d82cf2e39.JPG\" title=\"2.JPG\" alt=\"2.JPG\" width=\"726\" height=\"453\" style=\"width: 726px; height: 453px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/data/upload/ueditor/20180402/5ac1d83328fd6.JPG\" title=\"3.JPG\" alt=\"3.JPG\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">设计师将入户门厅的一面墙塑造成水纹波浪的造型，钢琴区就安排在这边，墙上方飞鸟造型的吊灯栩栩如生，这样木质、金属与科技的组合，经设计师塑性调色，显得优美而引人遐想：曼妙的音律响起，袅袅而上，伴着水波粼粼，撩拨一群海鸟随风起舞。这样的意境，怎能不令人形舒神逸。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 25px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/data/upload/ueditor/20180402/5ac1d85738cd7.JPG\" title=\"5.JPG\" alt=\"5.JPG\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-indent: 2em;\">拾级而上，是半开放式的厨房与餐厅。设计师在吊顶、地板和墙面的处理上几近质朴，不做华饰，整个空间的灵气都集中在用餐区。独特的造型吊顶极具科技感与空间想象力，餐桌与椅子造型轻盈、构架简练，与简约厚实的中岛台一轻盈一厚重，虚实相生，相映成趣。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/data/upload/ueditor/20180402/5ac1d85b9c353.JPG\" title=\"4.JPG\" alt=\"4.JPG\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-indent: 2em;\">设计师将本案的客厅设在餐厅之下的负一层，一方面与入户门厅的休息区错开，完成功能区上的合理分布；另一方面能充分利用空间，使得负一层的休闲功能完整而有延续性。</span><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-indent: 2em;\">在客厅的设计上，设计师采用了下沉式的做法，对客厅的空间布局进行了再打造，巧妙运用高低的分差手法隔离空间，从而形成独特的视觉感，打破了普通客厅的空旷及视觉单一感，使客厅更具层次，产生舒适与安全感。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><br/></p><p><img src=\"/data/upload/ueditor/20180410/5acc26954953e.JPG\" title=\"6.JPG\" alt=\"6.JPG\"/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">与客厅相邻的是品茶区，设计师使用一款简约大气的博古架嵌入墙间，既完成了风格和功能上的过渡转换，又巧妙的借助其镂空完成空间延续。品茶区也是下沉式的，进入其间，心仿佛也随之沉静下来。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">墙面使用了较为深沉的颜色，茶台与茶具木色生香，大窗运用框景和借景的手法，取得屋外一点景致，更添意境。远离城市的喧嚣与生活的忙碌，暂弃光怪陆离的形状与色彩，把盏一杯香茗，任丝丝幽香冲淡浮尘，沉淀思绪，体会人生。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 25px; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 25px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/data/upload/ueditor/20180402/5ac1d86ee0993.JPG\" title=\"7.JPG\" alt=\"7.JPG\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 25px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 25px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-indent: 2em;\">客厅外露天的休闲区更是将形状的运用推至极致，几个简单的矩形和整齐的条梁将整个区域规划齐整，带来整洁有序的空间感受，再辅以园林设计的手法，引入鱼水，顿添一抹灵动与生机。几何构造的坐具与圆形透明吊椅时尚美观，又不失一种构造的禅意。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-align: center; line-height: 25px; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 25px; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/data/upload/ueditor/20180402/5ac1d880d48e2.JPG\" title=\"8.JPG\" alt=\"8.JPG\" width=\"741\" height=\"507\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; width: 741px; height: 507px;\"/><br/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(165, 165, 165); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">项目地点：福建 福州</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(165, 165, 165); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">主创设计：李超、陈志曙<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: